  "Description": {
    "English": "Large-bore projectile launcher. Propels plasma shells designed for <span class=\"name name-stellar\">rapid ground excavation</span>.<br> <br>Charged with <span class=\"name name-fuel\">Unstable Plasma</span>. Warning: Explosive hole creation may also damage nearby organic matter.<br> <br>Press <span class=\"name name-img\">ALTATTACK</span> to activate.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "大口径炮弹发射器。为专为<span class=\"name name-stellar\">快速地下掘进</span>而设计的等离子炮弹提供动力。<br> <br>使用<span class=\"name name-fuel\">不稳定的等离子</span>充能。警告：爆破开孔可能会危害附近的有机物质。<br> <br>按<span class=\"name name-img\">ALTATTACK</span>启用。",
    "TencentChinese": "大口径炮弹发射器。为专为<span class=\"name name-stellar\">快速地下掘进</span>而设计的等离子炮弹提供动力。<br><br>使用<span class=\"name name-fuel\">不稳定的等离子</span>充能。警告：迸裂开孔可能会危害附近的有机物质。<br><br>按<span class=\"name name-img\">ALTATTACK</span>启用。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "大口徑射彈發射器。能射出電漿砲彈，專為<span class=\"name name-stellar\">迅速地表開挖</span>而設計。<br> <br>以<span class=\"name name-fuel\">不穩定電漿</span>充能。警告：開鑿出會爆炸的洞口可能傷及鄰近有機物質。<br> <br>按下 <span class=\"name name-img\">ALTATTACK</span> 來發動。"
  },
